//! OZONE Studio - Code Modality Pipeline (ID: 101)
//!
//! Analyzes code and creates structural graphs for:
//! - AST/parse tree structure
//! - Dependencies (imports, references)
//! - Function/class definitions
//! - Type information
//! - Call graphs

